Feature: PO Held-Out Idea-Mode Eval Tasks
  As the operator gating idea-mode go-live for the sovereign planning loop
  I want deterministic held-out eval tasks for the PO agent's idea and scope modes
  So that invented requirements are caught by pytest before the agent ever plans in front of James

  Background:
    Given the frozen po-heldout suite po-held-001 through po-held-004 remains unchanged
    And the pinned ProductRoadmap contract from the harness is in force

