  @key-example @smoke
  Scenario: A contract-clean idea-mode response passes the po-held-005 gate
    Given the thin idea brief for po-held-005-idea
    And a candidate response with exactly one think block followed by one fenced ProductRoadmap object
    And the roadmap declares mode "idea" with a null coverage score and no source references at any level
    And the roadmap carries at least 3 assumptions each with a falsifiable statement, a confidence tag, and a stated impact if wrong
    When the po-held-005 gate grades the response
